Instance Method# getCollectionType

DriverKit 19.0+macOS

```
IOHIDElementCollectionType getCollectionType();
```

## [Return Value](/documentation/hiddriverkit/iohidelement/getcollectiontype#return-value)

Returns the element type. Types are defined by the IOHIDElementCollectionType enumerator in - [`IOHIDElementCollectionType`](/documentation/hiddriverkit/iohidelementcollectiontype).
